content: I think I have a pretty decent rig, it's a PC with an Intel Core i7-9700K processor, NVIDIA GeForce RTX 3080 graphics card, 16 GB DDR4 3200 MHz RAM, and I'm running Windows 10. As for Rocket League, I'm more of a casual player, I just like playing with my friends and trying out new cars, but I've been trying to focus on aerials lately.
